name: Individual Bars 07
description:
Individual Bars 07 with a seed based on the owners tezos-addresses, renders differently for every owner/viewer.
First rendering is always based on the viewer-wallet-address.

Click/Tap 	= Cycle through the different variations
V 		= Toggle Audio-Visualizer
N 		= Toggle Noise

Or move mouse to upper quarter of OBJKT to reveal overlay with clickable/tappable toggles.

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. OBJKT uses p5js with p5.createloop and post5.
- @TeNinEightNFTs
